Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.40,0:00:08.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那之後我為了救真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.12,0:00:11.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,進行了無數次時間跳躍
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.17,0:00:21.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 不管使用什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.26,0:00:26.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理都…死了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.57,0:00:44.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算沒有萌郁他們的襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.41,0:00:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像被命運所殺一般
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.82,0:00:53.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎整個世界都串通好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.12,0:00:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要殺死真由理！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.55,0:01:05.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都沒動啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.05,0:01:07.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為電車停了嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.05,0:01:08.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請快一點
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.18,0:01:09.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說抄近路！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.55,0:01:11.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.47,0:01:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 真由喜的懷錶停了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.56,0:01:20.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好奇怪啊 明明剛剛才上過發條的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.40,0:01:21.56,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又來了 又來了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.66,0:01:30.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.87,0:01:39.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,死掉的是椎名真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.33,0:01:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部君…不 岡部倫太郎逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.30,0:01:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎麼做 不管用什麼辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.35,0:01:56.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她還是會死
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.48,0:02:00.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這簡直…就跟命運一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.06,0:02:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 這才是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.82,0:02:06.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.24,0:02:10.03,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(692,630)}steins gate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.24,0:02:10.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機關也好 命運石之門也好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.66,0:02:13.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命運的選擇也好！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.16,0:02:16.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這些東西根本…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.20,0:02:18.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就不存在！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.99,0:03:53.96,title,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(810,652)}形而下的壞死
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.42,0:03:55.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼一回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.96,0:03:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我解釋一下
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.50,0:03:59.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可是剛進個人路線啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.63,0:04:00.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少讓我存個檔嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.92,0:04:02.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我替你存
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.30,0:04:04.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之要離開秋葉原
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.97,0:04:05.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽到了沒？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.43,0:04:06.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.59,0:04:37.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理已經出發了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.14,0:04:41.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.39,0:04:46.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論怎樣讓真由理逃跑 結果都…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:51.61,tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}發生什麼事了？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.15,0:04:51.61,tip,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an7}之後要好好解釋清楚啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.73,0:04:50.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵件也是一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.94,0:04:51.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,郵件…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:56.54,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(640,630)}shinging finger
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.12,0:04:56.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃光的指壓師
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.42,0:05:00.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我得到了關於時間機器的新情報
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.88,0:05:03.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想跟你單獨談談
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.79,0:05:16.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許動
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.87,0:05:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,舉起雙手
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的真實身份是什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.23,0:05:38.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兼職撰稿人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.89,0:05:44.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道你們今晚會襲擊Lab並綁架我們
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.49,0:05:47.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會知道？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.15,0:05:48.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我是從未來回來的！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.03,0:05:49.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.12,0:05:51.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.28,0:05:53.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用郵件來說
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.04,0:05:54.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行 快回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.12,0:05:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們是SERN嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.87,0:05:57.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rounder
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.96,0:05:59.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rounder？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.13,0:06:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務是回收IBN5100
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.38,0:06:04.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它是被你們偷走的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.76,0:06:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.63,0:06:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別裝傻
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.72,0:06:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發送了D-MAIL之後…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.80,0:06:10.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.93,0:06:12.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為世界線的變動
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.68,0:06:15.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在的萌郁並沒有發送了D-MAIL的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.48,0:06:17.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要襲擊Lab
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.19,0:06:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,IBN5100已經不在那裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.19,0:06:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.78,0:06:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,理由有三個
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.45,0:06:30.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一 你們知道了不該知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.70,0:06:36.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第二 製造出了時間機器
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.33,0:06:43.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第三 你們想將它公諸於世
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連這種事都…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.10,0:06:51.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SERN已經知道這一切了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.89,0:06:55.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我收到的指示是由FB下達的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.52,0:06:56.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.94,0:06:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,SREN的內部組織嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,FB是我的…一切
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.95,0:07:09.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:11.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.45,0:07:15.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,約翰‧提托是你嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:19.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除你之外 很難想像是別人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.46,0:07:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.10,0:07:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.31,0:07:35.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為恐嚇電話 所有列車都停運了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.94,0:07:37.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都在計畫之中
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.11,0:07:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抓住牧瀨紅莉栖 橋田至
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.15,0:07:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外的都不需要
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.45,0:07:45.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.57,0:07:49.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等…等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.45,0:07:53.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託你了 別殺…別殺真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.04,0:07:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.75,0:07:57.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.50,0:08:01.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我並不是想揭露SERN的內情
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.67,0:08:03.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我把時間跳躍機器交給你們
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.51,0:08:05.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不公開任何我知道的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.59,0:08:06.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,任務開始
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.51,0:08:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 我什麼都願意做
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.47,0:08:12.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,求你了 我們只是因為好奇心…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.52,0:08:14.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像在玩一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.52,0:08:17.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…別殺…真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經太晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.36,0:08:25.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.49,0:08:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:32.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閉嘴！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.04,0:08:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.46,0:08:40.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.32,0:09:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.95,0:09:04.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道在打瞌睡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.91,0:09:06.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.95,0:09:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經…受夠了！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.17,0:09:14.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.09,0:09:17.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.84,0:09:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不至於毀掉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.80,0:09:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是已經決定不進行時間跳躍了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.18,0:09:26.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了啊 這麼突然
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.81,0:09:28.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是要出門買東西嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.60,0:09:29.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Party的…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.23,0:09:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Party…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.73,0:09:34.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等 岡部
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.15,0:09:40.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哢嗒哢嗒 新幹線
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.24,0:09:43.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不對吧 新幹線是白色啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.87,0:09:48.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 岡…凶真先生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.79,0:09:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.33,0:09:55.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理醬的話 剛才…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.21,0:09:56.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.05,0:09:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管是她來這裡邀請你參加Party
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.01,0:10:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是為了COSPLAY的同伴 在回Lab前繞了路
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.39,0:10:07.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是她很期待這次的Party
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.39,0:10:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都知道
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.36,0:10:17.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:20.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.82,0:10:23.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是我卻…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.00,0:10:30.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種地方做什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.88,0:10:35.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅莉栖
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.50,0:10:39.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,第一次正經地叫了我的名字啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.42,0:10:40.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.51,0:10:42.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 是將要發生什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.68,0:10:48.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是時間跳躍回來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.48,0:10:52.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一切都是我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.31,0:10:53.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,岡部
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.57,0:10:56.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全部都是我的責任
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.86,0:11:00.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒叫桶子去入侵就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.41,0:11:04.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒說想要製造時間機器就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:07.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是沒讓萌郁成為LabMem就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.58,0:11:10.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都怪我…讓真由理她…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.63,0:11:18.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是亂來啊 笨蛋
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.01,0:11:23.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間跳躍機器不一定是絕對安全的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.22,0:11:28.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞不好 連你自己都可能消失掉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.18,0:11:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從根本上來說 人類是時間性的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.19,0:11:36.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,海德格啊 我剛才也正想這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.98,0:11:39.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這話就是聽你說的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.28,0:11:42.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總覺得有點不太對勁
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.28,0:11:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像腦子被偷窺了一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.91,0:11:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 所謂時間跳躍可能就是這麼一回事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.08,0:11:52.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我該如何是好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.04,0:11:54.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Lab會在幾點遭到襲擊？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.92,0:11:56.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,7點半後
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.25,0:12:01.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理為什麼會死 我能想到好幾種可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.13,0:12:04.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是現在沒時間說
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.13,0:12:09.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧 真由理是重要的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.64,0:12:10.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也想救她
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.35,0:12:14.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.52,0:12:15.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要道歉
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.31,0:12:19.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是想助你一臂之力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.65,0:12:23.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是自稱「瘋狂的科學狂人」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.98,0:12:26.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是說要改變什麼世界構造嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.99,0:12:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「當然了 哇哈哈哈哈哈…」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.37,0:12:37.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣才對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.93,0:12:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間設定在五個小時前
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.51,0:13:00.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是剛剛做好時間跳躍機器的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.52,0:13:01.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是跳躍到那之前的話
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.14,0:13:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,機器就有可能無法做成了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.44,0:13:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你跳躍到那時
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.03,0:13:11.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,時間跳躍機器一旦完成
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.20,0:13:13.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓大家解散
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.82,0:13:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後告訴我剛才的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.07,0:13:17.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要你說自己是來自未來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.57,0:13:18.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該會相信的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.28,0:13:20.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.99,0:13:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己最瞭解自己了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.04,0:13:28.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再說了 開發出時間跳躍機的可是本小姐da☆ze！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說對自己的機器很有信心嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.96,0:13:33.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.13,0:13:36.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才看到你的時候 我就確信了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:39.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是時間跳躍回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.22,0:13:42.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以防萬一 定個暗號吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:47.27,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(857,630)}My fork
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.89,0:13:47.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我現在最想要的東西是「便攜叉子」
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:51.40,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(684,630)}My fork
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.44,0:13:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想要「便攜叉子」嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:54.07,english,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(565,630)}My spoon
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.44,0:13:54.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 「便攜湯匙」我已經有了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.78,0:13:56.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重點不是這個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.65,0:13:58.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.07,0:14:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五小時前的我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.29,0:14:09.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道你叫過我「紅莉栖」的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.84,0:14:22.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能替我拿一下這個嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.39,0:14:24.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.26,0:14:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.39,0:14:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這樣筆直把它展開
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.48,0:14:32.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個蝴蝶結真可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.39,0:14:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.52,0:14:35.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 克莉絲醬要不也試試看？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.85,0:14:38.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次的CM還有別的COS服哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.22,0:14:40.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,COSPLAY嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,莫非你有興趣？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.89,0:14:44.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才沒有！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.43,0:14:47.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然要在別人面前穿這種衣服…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.50,0:14:52.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦…五小時之前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.53,0:14:54.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真由理還沒有出門
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.72,0:14:58.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在真由理完成COS服的同時 時間跳躍機器也應該…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.62,0:15:01.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完成啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.54,0:15:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我贏了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.29,0:15:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實我是在跟你們比賽哦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.92,0:15:07.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 被打敗了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.71,0:15:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 我們也已經弄好了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.30,0:15:11.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣就完工了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.72,0:15:13.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.34,0:15:14.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不做實驗！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.01,0:15:20.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,糟糕 說得太突然了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.14,0:15:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:26.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家都累了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.44,0:15:30.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詳細情況之後再說 今天就先解散
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.49,0:15:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛皿
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.32,0:15:35.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,牛皿一份
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.61,0:15:36.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎麼在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.03,0:15:40.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好在點菜的時候 收到了郵件
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.28,0:15:42.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到你是這裡的常客啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.00,0:15:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才…才不是常客啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.50,0:15:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真由理告訴我的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.50,0:15:49.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你到底想說什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:54.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先是突然讓大家解散 現在又發郵件給我
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.71,0:16:00.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實 我是從五小時後的未來回來的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:03.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊 真可笑
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.81,0:16:05.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.64,0:16:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,跟你之前說的完全不一樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.69,0:16:09.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼「我應該會相信」啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.85,0:16:11.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你瞎說什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.02,0:16:16.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會說「應該相信」這種毫無根據的話吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.99,0:16:17.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.32,0:16:21.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「再說了 開發出時間跳躍機器的可是本小姐da☆ze！」
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.12,0:16:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還一臉得意的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.66,0:16:24.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傻不傻啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.95,0:16:29.92,neta1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(15,20,15,10,0,200)\pos(15,10)\fad(300, 300)}ワロス
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.62,0:16:30.12,neta2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fscx0\pos(15,20)\t(0,200,1,\fscx65)\t(5300,0,1,\fscx0)}———
